description:
Year/Date Of Issue: 2013
Version: 4.25
Developer: AMS Software
Interface language: Russian
Tabletka: Cured
System requirements: Windows XP, Vista, 7, 8
CPU: 1GHz, 512 Mb RAM
Description:
Photoshow is easy to use program for creating music slideshows with beautiful transition effects. Allows you to add unlimited number of photos, insert captions and credits, to use skins, and much more. Prepared a slide show you can save it to an EXE file, screensaver or video, including HD. Fotoshow has the convenient interface in Russian language and is easy to master. Create an unforgettable slide show of high quality in just a few minutes! The program allows you to view the slide show on your computer, and also convert video format. The new version includes the burn slideshows to DVD.
Opportunities:
- User-friendly interface to add photos and control the slideshow.
- Select transition effects. This catalogue presents over one hundred original effects.
- Edit slide and add text.
- Fit for the slide show. The function of the "virtual screen".
- Select the format to save your slide show video, DVD, screensaver or EXE.
* Lock the program access to the Internet by a firewall!
